{
  "stem": "1680.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 445.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The second advantage was the trucks came to pick up the merchandise, they-- and they brought in bread from the-- from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they always had an extra few breads so we could buy from them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody knew, so we could help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We helped our relatives there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have some friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we always had an advantage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the second advantage was the manager from Madrich by the name Titsch-- he was a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was probably an invalid, because he was limping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he didn't go to the army so he had this job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So he went every day to-- to Krakow of a night and came back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nobody checked his trunks in the car-- what he has there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, he says to Margot-- [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This mean, why do you so pale?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she says, you know that-- what the conditions we are.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, do you have some money?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he says, give me a little note.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'll see-- he had these people in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They bought everything on the black market.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he brought us almost every week one little extra package.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was-- this was an advantage, because we could-- we had better-- better nourishment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then came-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was going on like this for-- from September 1943 until-- yeah, until 1944.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The end of October '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the meantime, we were called-- Mengele came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know who Mengele is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The doctor, the-- from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wants to make-- in the meantime, they had the kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They-- they took all the kids on a-- they had loudspeakers all over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they took all the kids there [INAUDIBLE] still to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
